Geraldine Court https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Geraldine_Court 0 Geraldine Court (born Geraldine Oldenboorn, 28 July 1942 – 20 November 2010) was an American actress, known for her appearances in The Doctors, Guiding Light, As the World Turns, Another World, and All My Children. She was also, during a brief time, a writer for the serial Loving.
